db.statement: SELECT "opbeans_orderline"."product_id", "opbeans_orderline"."amount", "opbeans_product"."sku", "opbeans_product"."name", "opbeans_product"."description", "opbeans_product"."product_type_id", "opbeans_product"."stock", "opbeans_product"."cost", "opbeans_product"."selling_price" FROM "opbeans_orderline" INNER JOIN "opbeans_product" ON ("opbeans_orderline"."product_id" = "opbeans_product"."id") WHERE "opbeans_orderline"."order_id" = %s
